microsoft-ads-cli (personal fork)

This is an personal rebuild of microsoft-ads-cli
(https://github.com/Bin-Huang/microsoft-ads-cli) by Benn Huang,
used under the Apache-2.0 license.

Modifications by Alessandro Moretti (2026):
- Rebuilt on the google-ads-cli command structure for 1:1 functional parity
- Added "auth login" browser OAuth2 flow with automatic token refresh
- Added synchronous stats commands (campaign/ad-group/ad/keyword) that
  submit, poll, download, and parse Bing Reporting API reports to JSON
- Added account-hierarchy, ad-group/ad detail, shared negative keyword
  lists and list items, ad extension library and associations,
  conversion goals by IDs, and a read-only raw "api" escape hatch
- Restructured command signatures to account-id-first positionals

The original copyright and license are retained in LICENSE.
